01:00:48,320 --> 01:00:50,440
Power on zone 3 again
and continue with zone 4.

734
01:01:01,760 --> 01:01:02,960
What sort of signs?

735
01:01:03,640 --> 01:01:05,240
I'm sorry?

736
01:01:09,720 --> 01:01:13,360
If the Holy Father was given
an overdose of Tinzaparin,

737
01:01:13,920 --> 01:01:15,960
what signs would his body bear?

738
01:01:17,760 --> 01:01:19,400
Bleeding of the oral mucosa.

739
01:01:21,080 --> 01:01:22,440
His tongue.

740
01:01:22,760 --> 01:01:26,040
Post-mortem, the blood congeals,
then turns the inside of the mouth black.

741
01:01:28,080 --> 01:01:29,920
Even after fourteen days?

742
01:01:30,760 --> 01:01:33,480
It wouldn't show up until at
least a week after his death.

743
01:01:38,600 --> 01:01:40,080
He was very important to me.

744
01:01:42,080 --> 01:01:43,640
Yeah, I understand.

745
01:01:48,440 --> 01:01:50,600
Will you come with me, please?

746
01:01:58,680 --> 01:02:00,428
Signore, would you
organize a security team

747
01:02:00,480 --> 01:02:02,360
to escort Ms. Vetra and
myself down to the crypt?

748
01:02:02,560 --> 01:02:04,320
Yes, sir. We'll leave immediately.

749
01:02:22,960 --> 01:02:24,840
Do you smoke?

750
01:02:26,280 --> 01:02:27,880
A little bit.

751
01:02:28,200 --> 01:02:31,120
You better sit down
before you keel over.

752
01:02:36,920 --> 01:02:41,760
What does this say in Italian?
Ecstasy of Saint Theresa. Right there.

753
01:02:44,360 --> 01:02:47,000
Moved at suggestion of the artist.

754
01:02:47,640 --> 01:02:51,720
Moved? To another church?
At the suggestion of Bernini?

755
01:02:51,760 --> 01:02:53,320
I don't know.

756
01:02:55,640 --> 01:02:59,960
Here. Translate all of this for me,
and I'll buy you a pack of smokes.

757
01:03:00,012 --> 01:03:02,600
I'm looking for a reference of fire.

758
01:03:04,520 --> 01:03:07,520
- Seraphim, meaning "the fiery one".
- Right.

759
01:03:10,000 --> 01:03:13,920
His great golden spear. A point of fire.

760
01:03:15,320 --> 01:03:19,320
Then "woman left completely afire."

761
01:03:19,360 --> 01:03:23,400
The ecstasy of Saint Theresa.
Saint Theresa on fire.

762
01:03:23,452 --> 01:03:26,040
So, this sculpture was
moved to this church?

763
01:03:27,720 --> 01:03:30,560
Why are they shuting down the system?
They know we're down here.

764
01:03:31,240 --> 01:03:34,200
If there's no power, there's no oxygen.

765
01:03:35,160 --> 01:03:37,800
- Can we get out?
- The door is electronic.

766
01:03:41,440 --> 01:03:43,200
Well, that's disappointing.

767
01:03:44,560 --> 01:03:47,560
- Where are we going?
- To see my father.

768
01:03:47,920 --> 01:03:49,400
I don't understand.

769
01:03:49,440 --> 01:03:52,240
I was orphaned when I
was nine years of age.

770
01:03:52,400 --> 01:03:56,840
A bombing in Ulster, the UVF protesting
the visit of a Catholic Archbishop.

771
01:03:56,920 --> 01:04:01,160
The Archbishop felt responsible
and he adopted me the following day.

772
01:04:01,440 --> 01:04:04,000
I was raised by him and by the Church.

773
01:04:04,560 --> 01:04:06,920
He was the wisest man I ever met.

774
01:04:07,360 --> 01:04:11,080
Even when I was young and stubborn,
I wanted to be ordained,

775
01:04:11,120 --> 01:04:14,560
but I was brought up in Italy
so I also wanted to do my military service.

776
01:04:14,612 --> 01:04:16,480
I wanted to fight.

777
01:04:16,920 --> 01:04:19,868
He told me, "Learn to fly."

778
01:04:19,920 --> 01:04:23,800
So, I joined the Aeronautica Militari.
Flew helicopters.

779
01:04:23,852 --> 01:04:26,200
Bringing the wounded back to hospitals.

780
01:04:26,240 --> 01:04:29,320
- He was a great man.
- Your father died.

781
01:04:30,160 --> 01:04:31,840
Fourteen days ago.

782
01:04:32,760 --> 01:04:34,640
Headquarters, you hear me?

783
01:04:35,200 --> 01:04:37,868
The flow is completed.
Oxygen level is very low.

784
01:04:37,920 --> 01:04:41,400
- Answer, please. Anybody hear me?
- Did you get anything?

785
01:04:41,440 --> 01:04:45,120
No. The walls are lead lined.
There's no signal.

786
01:07:59,520 --> 01:08:00,560
This way.

787
01:08:08,440 --> 01:08:12,440
If the Holy Father was murdered,
the implications are profound.

788
01:08:12,492 --> 01:08:14,708
Vatican security is impenetrable.

789
01:08:14,760 --> 01:08:17,320
No one from the outside
could've got anywhere near him.

790
01:08:17,680 --> 01:08:21,400
It was someone on the inside.
We can trust no one.

791
01:08:23,360 --> 01:08:27,320
On my screen, no response in zone 7.

792
01:08:27,360 --> 01:08:31,320
We rechon that the
battery will soon be empty

793
01:08:31,560 --> 01:08:33,840
and the device will explode
shortly before midnight.

794
01:08:55,440 --> 01:08:57,040
Holy Father...

795
01:08:57,960 --> 01:09:02,000
when I was young, you've told me the
voice in my heart was God's voice.

796
01:09:02,040 --> 01:09:05,480
You said I should follow
it no matter how painful.

797
01:09:05,532 --> 01:09:06,840
Forgive me.

798
01:09:08,560 --> 01:09:10,160
Please, give me strength.

799
01:09:11,360 --> 01:09:15,960
What I do, I do in the name
of everything you believed.

800
01:10:06,240 --> 01:10:08,080
God help us.

801
01:10:20,560 --> 01:10:23,320
Santa Maria della Vittoria.
Do you know it?

802
01:10:23,800 --> 01:10:26,200
- Yes, I do.
- It's the next church.

803
01:10:42,480 --> 01:10:44,500
I think someone just tried to kill me.

804
01:10:44,552 --> 01:10:46,520
Professor, I promise you,
we had no idea.

805
01:10:46,572 --> 01:10:47,668
- He knows I'm here?
- Yes.

806
01:10:47,720 --> 01:10:49,640
You heard me ask permission.
You gave me an escort.

807
01:10:49,692 --> 01:10:50,708
Yes, but we had no idea

808
01:10:50,760 --> 01:10:53,960
that portions of our white zones
were crosswired with that building.

809
01:10:54,960 --> 01:10:56,780
Commander Richter was
extending the search.

810
01:10:56,832 --> 01:10:58,600
If he had known the archives
were on that grid,

811
01:10:58,652 --> 01:10:59,960
he never would have killed the power.

812
01:11:01,040 --> 01:11:03,080
But there is the other possibility.

813
01:11:03,280 --> 01:11:06,160
Is it conceivable the Illuminati...

814
01:11:06,720 --> 01:11:09,200
have infiltrated the Swiss Guard?

815
01:11:11,840 --> 01:11:13,240
Perhaps.

816
01:11:23,400 --> 01:11:25,240
The journals. Where are they?

817
01:11:27,560 --> 01:11:29,880
Who took the journals from this desk?

818
01:11:40,000 --> 01:11:42,800
Signore, this is unacceptable.

819
01:11:43,480 --> 01:11:46,560
For a Camerlengo to enter the
chapel once conclave has begun.

820
01:11:46,612 --> 01:11:47,588
Forgive me.

821
01:11:47,640 --> 01:11:49,480
There's been a development.

822
01:12:00,040 --> 01:12:02,708
His Holiness Celestine was murdered!

823
01:12:02,760 --> 01:12:06,640
Is it so inconceivable
that it will happen again?

824
01:12:06,692 --> 01:12:09,560
Signori, please, a moment.
Please. Signori.

825
01:12:12,040 --> 01:12:14,480
Our church is at war.

826
01:12:15,520 --> 01:12:18,800
We are under attack from an old enemy.

827
01:12:19,160 --> 01:12:20,960
The Illuminati.

828
01:12:21,480 --> 01:12:24,000
They have struck us from within.

829
01:12:24,052 --> 01:12:26,200
Murdering our Holy Father!

830
01:12:26,240 --> 01:12:30,760
And threatening us all with destruction
at the hands of their new God 'Science'.

831
01:12:30,880 --> 01:12:34,120
They call it retribution.
They think it justified...

832
01:12:34,160 --> 01:12:38,280
because of the Church's attacks on men of
science in the distant past and it's true.

833
01:12:39,000 --> 01:12:44,080
Since the days of Galileo, this church has
tried to slow the relentless march of progress.

834
01:12:44,132 --> 01:12:46,320
Sometimes with misguided means.

835
01:12:47,840 --> 01:12:49,920
But science and
religion are not enemies.

836
01:12:51,560 --> 01:12:56,240
There are simply some things that
science is just too young to understand.

837
01:12:56,560 --> 01:12:58,400
So the Church pleads, "Stop."

838
01:12:58,920 --> 01:13:00,200
"Slow down."

839
01:13:00,360 --> 01:13:01,720
"Think. Wait."

840
01:13:01,920 --> 01:13:03,760
And, for this, they call us backwards.

841
01:13:04,880 --> 01:13:06,640
But who is more ignorant?

842
01:13:06,960 --> 01:13:08,960
The man who cannot define lightning...

843
01:13:09,360 --> 01:13:12,440
or the man who does not respect
its natural awesome power?

844
01:13:13,520 --> 01:13:15,680
The battle is well under way, signori.

845
01:13:16,400 --> 01:13:18,360
We must defend ourselves.

846
01:13:18,560 --> 01:13:21,120
But, what if this time, we fight
their stealth with openness?

847
01:13:21,320 --> 01:13:24,000
Combat their wicked
scheme with simple truth.

848
01:13:24,200 --> 01:13:27,120
And end this brutish
battle once and for all.

849
01:13:27,320 --> 01:13:30,160
If the outside world could
see this church as I do,

850
01:13:30,360 --> 01:13:32,240
looking beyond the
ritual of these walls,

851
01:13:32,440 --> 01:13:34,960
they would see a modern miracle.

852
01:13:35,200 --> 01:13:38,760
A brotherhood of
imperfect, simple souls...

853
01:13:38,960 --> 01:13:41,920
who want nothing more than to be voices of compassion

854
01:13:41,972 --> 01:13:43,800
in a world spinning out of control.

855
01:13:46,040 --> 01:13:48,480
Signori, I ask..

856
01:13:49,720 --> 01:13:51,440
I pray...

857
01:13:52,680 --> 01:13:54,960
that you break this conclave.

858
01:13:55,280 --> 01:13:56,640
Open the doors,

859
01:13:57,760 --> 01:13:59,520
evacuate St. Peter's Square

860
01:14:00,120 --> 01:14:01,800
and tell the world the truth.

861
01:14:37,320 --> 01:14:38,920
Get him down.

862
01:14:50,600 --> 01:14:53,080
There. There, that
chain. On that pulley.

863
01:14:53,320 --> 01:14:54,720
This bench. Get this pew off
here and make it a ladder.

864
01:16:16,720 --> 01:16:18,120
Vatican Police.

865
01:17:20,160 --> 01:17:22,880
My son...

866
01:17:22,920 --> 01:17:26,360
God answers all prayers, but...

867
01:17:27,160 --> 01:17:29,560
sometimes His answer is no.

868
01:17:30,720 --> 01:17:33,440
The College will not break conclave.

869
01:17:34,560 --> 01:17:38,508
May I suggest...
you direct your energies

870
01:17:38,560 --> 01:17:42,160
to helping the Swiss Guard
find this explosive device.

871
01:17:42,212 --> 01:17:43,840
If it exists.

872
01:17:45,000 --> 01:17:47,720
And leave Church leadership...

873
01:17:49,440 --> 01:17:51,280
to its leaders.

874
01:18:03,360 --> 01:18:04,600
Eminence.

875
01:18:06,840 --> 01:18:09,120
There is a growing fear

876
01:18:09,840 --> 01:18:11,948
that without the four Preferiti

877
01:18:12,000 --> 01:18:15,200
it defers much authority
for any candidate.

878
01:18:15,252 --> 01:18:16,960
It will not be possible,

879
01:18:17,280 --> 01:18:19,440
- unless...
- Speak plainly.

880
01:18:20,720 --> 01:18:24,440
It is the recommendation of many
that you asked to be removed...

881
01:18:24,492 --> 01:18:26,680
from your post as Great Elector.

882
01:18:26,960 --> 01:18:33,400
Thereby making yourself eligible
to wear the Ring of the Fisherman.

883
01:18:34,680 --> 01:18:37,960
Well, if it is God's will.

884
01:18:45,520 --> 01:18:47,520
May His will be done.

885
01:19:00,320 --> 01:19:02,240
Here! I hear someone.

886
01:19:04,520 --> 01:19:06,160
Remove the lid.

887
01:19:08,920 --> 01:19:09,960
Come on.

888
01:19:14,320 --> 01:19:15,920
Signore, are you okay?

889
01:19:24,240 --> 01:19:26,108
I know he is there.

890
01:19:26,160 --> 01:19:29,148
Madam, it is necessary
that you remain quiet.

891
01:19:29,200 --> 01:19:33,000
Don't tell me that I should remain calm.
I want to know what he will do.

892
01:19:37,520 --> 01:19:39,400
Commander, here's Ms. Vetra.

893
01:19:40,880 --> 01:19:43,400
Those journals are private property.
I demand that you return them to me.

894
01:19:43,452 --> 01:19:46,560
They're material evidence
in a Vatican investigation.

895
01:19:48,840 --> 01:19:49,948
I am an Italian citizen.

896
01:19:50,000 --> 01:19:53,000
My rights do not end just
because I crossed the other side.

897
01:19:53,052 --> 01:19:56,000
This is not Italy.
It's not even Rome. It's the Vatican.

898
01:19:56,052 --> 01:19:57,988
A country with its own laws.

899
01:19:58,040 --> 01:20:01,520
And when those journals passed the
border, they became my property.

900
01:20:01,572 --> 01:20:03,240
I will give them back to you

901
01:20:03,640 --> 01:20:06,680
when I've decided they contain
nothing of value to the investigation.

902
01:20:06,732 --> 01:20:09,040
Do you have something to
hide, Commandante Richter?

903
01:20:11,960 --> 01:20:13,880
Do you, Dr. Vetra?

904
01:20:35,520 --> 01:20:37,880
If it were up to me,
it wouldn't be this way.

905
01:20:39,520 --> 01:20:42,080
It's a sin to kill with pain.

906
01:20:43,320 --> 01:20:45,480
It's a sin to kill
without reason, Father.

907
01:20:51,760 --> 01:20:53,120
They made me a sinner.

908
01:21:12,880 --> 01:21:14,560
Saint Theresa on fire.

909
01:21:17,960 --> 01:21:18,920
Professor Langdon?

910
01:21:20,560 --> 01:21:22,680
- What direction is that?
- West, I think.

911
01:21:22,880 --> 01:21:24,720
"Across Rome the mystic
elements unfold."

912
01:21:26,840 --> 01:21:31,640
Piazza Barba Rini is here.
Saint Theresa is here.

913
01:21:32,560 --> 01:21:34,680
Where is the Santa Maria del Popolo,
the first altar of science?

914
01:21:34,880 --> 01:21:36,080
- Santa Maria del Popolo?
- Yes.

915
01:21:38,320 --> 01:21:39,480
Thank you.

916
01:21:40,320 --> 01:21:41,720
St. Peter's is here.

917
01:21:42,600 --> 01:21:44,080
We are here.

918
01:21:46,160 --> 01:21:47,760
A church with water.

919
01:21:49,800 --> 01:21:51,000
Wait. Wait, wait.

920
01:21:51,800 --> 01:21:53,200
Across Rome.

921
01:21:54,840 --> 01:21:57,120
The poem must mean it's
literally across Rome.

922
01:21:57,880 --> 01:21:58,400
Professor Langdon.

923
01:21:58,520 --> 01:22:01,160
Commander Richter has ordered me to
escort you to the Vatican immediately.

924
01:22:01,400 --> 01:22:05,960
Piazza Navona. Earth. Air. Fire. Water.

925
01:22:06,400 --> 01:22:08,160
"A-Cross" Rome.

926
01:22:08,680 --> 01:22:10,240
Bernini's Four Rivers.

927
01:22:11,880 --> 01:22:14,840
Professor Langdon, the Vatican insists
that I have to take you back immediately.

928
01:22:15,040 --> 01:22:17,320
The Vatican is about to see its
fourth cardinal murdered tonight.

929
01:22:17,520 --> 01:22:18,600
Now, look.

930
01:22:19,400 --> 01:22:22,240
You can do as they say and
force me back to the Vatican,

931
01:22:22,560 --> 01:22:24,840
where we can all mourn
his death together.

932
01:22:25,040 --> 01:22:27,080
Or you can show me how real cops act

933
01:22:27,320 --> 01:22:30,640
and take me to Piazza Navona,
where we still might be able to stop it.

934
01:22:34,320 --> 01:22:36,280
Oh. By all means, let's talk it over.

935
01:22:37,520 --> 01:22:39,240
In fourteen minutes,
he's going to be dead.

936
01:22:45,040 --> 01:22:46,560
Okay. This way, Professor.

937
01:22:55,280 --> 01:22:56,520
Yes, Padre?

938
01:22:56,920 --> 01:22:59,720
At 11:15, if the church
is still in peril,

939
01:23:00,840 --> 01:23:02,960
give the order to
evacuate the cardinals.

940
01:23:04,080 --> 01:23:05,480
But with dignity.

941
01:23:06,320 --> 01:23:09,200
Let them walk out into St. Peter's
Square with their heads held high.

942
01:23:10,160 --> 01:23:12,280
We don't want the last
image of this church to be

943
01:23:12,332 --> 01:23:14,400
of frightened old men
sneaking out the back door.

944
01:23:31,320 --> 01:23:32,640
"Where the angels guide thee..."

945
01:23:38,440 --> 01:23:40,240
There it is. There it is.

946
01:23:40,320 --> 01:23:42,880
Professor, I know this fountain.
There is no angel.

947
01:23:43,080 --> 01:23:45,360
The dove. The angel of peace.

948
01:23:45,920 --> 01:23:47,520
And it's looking in what direction?

949
01:23:48,280 --> 01:23:49,520
Uh... east, I think.

950
01:24:00,720 --> 01:24:03,600
Professor, just wait here. Stay put.

951
01:24:39,720 --> 01:24:41,320
Good evening. Can you help me?

952
01:24:42,360 --> 01:24:44,160
I need a doctor.

953
01:24:59,840 --> 01:25:01,040
Come here.

954
01:25:04,120 --> 01:25:05,240
Calm down. Don't shoot.

955
01:25:42,160 --> 01:25:44,120
Hey!

956
01:25:57,840 --> 01:26:00,000
Help! Somebody help!

957
01:26:37,880 --> 01:26:39,200
Help! Somebody!

958
01:27:50,720 --> 01:27:51,720
Cardinal Baja.

959
01:27:52,720 --> 01:27:53,640
Cardinal Baja.

960
01:27:54,320 --> 01:27:55,360
Si?

961
01:27:55,520 --> 01:27:57,160
Where was he hiding you?

962
01:27:58,160 --> 01:27:59,920
The Church of Illumination.
Where is it?

963
01:28:01,480 --> 01:28:03,760
Castel Sant'Angelo.

964
01:28:05,280 --> 01:28:07,080
Castle of the Angel.

965
01:28:28,560 --> 01:28:30,720
Sir, there's news about Cardinal Baja.

966
01:28:31,960 --> 01:28:34,800
The cardinal told Langdon he was
being held in Castel Sant'Angelo.

967
01:28:35,600 --> 01:28:37,640
If Langdon's right,
that's where the bomb is.

968
01:28:38,440 --> 01:28:40,880
- Send everyone we can spare.
- And you?

969
01:28:41,440 --> 01:28:42,480
I'm staying here.

970
01:28:55,640 --> 01:28:56,720
Vittoria.

971
01:28:58,080 --> 01:28:59,880
- You're all right?
- I'm all right, yes. What about you?

972
01:28:59,932 --> 01:29:01,680
I just heard about
Olivetti on the radio.

973
01:29:01,732 --> 01:29:02,640
I'm all right. I'm okay.

974
01:29:08,440 --> 01:29:10,560
Robert, we can't trust Richter.

975
01:29:10,600 --> 01:29:11,668
He took Silvano's journals.

976
01:29:11,720 --> 01:29:14,200
There must be something in
there he doesn't want us to see.

977
01:29:14,240 --> 01:29:16,360
The head of the Swiss Guard.

978
01:29:17,760 --> 01:29:20,480
From the Castel Sant'Angelo.
It's close enough so the wireless signal

979
01:29:20,532 --> 01:29:22,200
from that camera
could still reach the Vatican.

980
01:29:23,960 --> 01:29:26,840
The Church of Illumination
is somewhere here

981
01:29:27,400 --> 01:29:29,400
and your canister is inside it.

982
01:29:49,160 --> 01:29:50,600
Come with me.

983
01:29:54,640 --> 01:29:57,788
For 400 years, the Illuminati
met right under the Church's nose.

984
01:29:57,840 --> 01:30:01,000
The Vatican used this as a hideout
and as a prison for their enemies.

