1004
01:32:45,280 --> 01:32:47,760
An ancient escape route.

1005
01:32:50,040 --> 01:32:51,440
Oh, God.

1006
01:32:53,360 --> 01:32:54,440
Here.

1007
01:32:57,040 --> 01:32:58,760
Look.

1008
01:33:30,240 --> 01:33:31,508
Get on the radio.

