1013
01:33:48,120 --> 01:33:50,800
The canister should be
lit by artificial light.

1014
01:34:13,840 --> 01:34:15,000
It's not here, Robert.

1015
01:34:15,080 --> 01:34:17,360
"The shining star at the end of the path."
It has to be.

1016
01:34:17,760 --> 01:34:19,520
It's not here.

1017
01:34:19,720 --> 01:34:21,840
What's the poem say?
- Nothing.

1018
01:34:21,920 --> 01:34:24,880
Nothing. It's all over.
There was just four lines,

1019
01:34:24,960 --> 01:34:27,000
each one describing...

1020
