There's a fifth brand.

1021
01:34:37,760 --> 01:34:39,760
It's not an ambigram.
It's just two crossed keys.

1022
01:34:40,160 --> 01:34:42,640
- The symbol for the Vatican.
- No.

1023
01:34:43,640 --> 01:34:46,800
No, the papacy.
They intend to kill him.

1024
01:34:46,840 --> 01:34:49,028
Before they destroy the Vatican,

1025
01:34:49,080 --> 01:34:51,000
they're going to brand
and kill the pope himself.

1026
01:34:51,040 --> 01:34:51,760
There is no pope.

1027
01:34:51,880 --> 01:34:53,640
"Tempo Sede Vacante."

1028
01:34:54,160 --> 01:34:55,880
The Camerlengo.

1029
01:34:57,520 --> 01:34:59,760
- We have to warn him.
- Take a step back, please.

1030
01:35:01,280 --> 01:35:03,520
Take your cell phone from your pocket.

1031
01:35:06,680 --> 01:35:08,400
Throw it in the fire.

1032
01:35:18,800 --> 01:35:20,588
Murderer.

1033
01:35:20,640 --> 01:35:22,600
You know, when they call me,

1034
01:35:23,240 --> 01:35:24,308
and they all call me,

1035
