I've had several chances
to eliminate you tonight.

1041
01:35:47,120 --> 01:35:49,400
You're still alive
because you have no weapon.

1042
01:35:49,452 --> 01:35:50,908
And they didn't ask me to kill you.

1043
01:35:50,960 --> 01:35:54,120
But if you pursue me,
it is another matter.

1044
01:36:01,080 --> 01:36:02,280
Be careful.

1045
01:36:02,440 --> 01:36:04,440
These are men of God.

1046
01:36:16,880 --> 01:36:18,080
The Camerlengo.

1047
01:36:26,120 --> 01:36:28,520
