1048
01:36:36,440 --> 01:36:37,480
Here. Here.

1049
01:38:01,120 --> 01:38:03,400
- I need to see the Camerlengo.
- He is not available.

1050
01:38:03,452 --> 01:38:05,680
- I demand to see the Camerlengo!
- He is not available.

1051
01:38:07,360 --> 01:38:08,760
We'll see about that.

1052
01:38:18,000 --> 01:38:20,600
Oh. It's a chiusa chiave.
It's a one way portal.

1053
01:38:20,640 --> 01:38:22,800
The only entrance is on the other side.

1054
01:38:23,320 --> 01:38:25,440
No. Hey! Help!

1055
01:38:33,520 --> 01:38:35,920
This is Robert Langdon and
Dr. Vetra. Open the door.

1056
01:38:48,800 --> 01:38:50,680
The Camerlengo is in danger.

1057
01:39:03,840 --> 01:39:06,400
He's the one. He's got a gun.

1058
01:39:09,880 --> 01:39:12,120
- Illuminatus!
- You bastard.

1059
01:39:12,680 --> 01:39:13,360
Illuminatus!

1060
01:39:13,520 --> 01:39:14,920
You bastard!

1061
01:39:22,760 --> 01:39:23,720
Padre?

1062
01:39:23,800 --> 01:39:27,240
Order the evacuation.
We only have nineteen minutes.

1063
01:39:30,960 --> 01:39:32,600
Here. He's...

1064
01:39:32,680 --> 01:39:35,000
And get the helicopter for
the older cardinals, right?

1065
01:39:35,052 --> 01:39:35,680
Yes, sir.

1066
01:39:48,920 --> 01:39:49,920
Robert?

1067
01:39:50,080 --> 01:39:52,840
The brand, the symbol.
Could it have another meaning?

1068
01:39:59,200 --> 01:40:02,400
Crossed keys,
but those were upside down.

1069
01:40:02,452 --> 01:40:04,000
St. Peter.

1070
01:40:04,880 --> 01:40:06,680
The first pope...

1071
01:40:07,760 --> 01:40:10,588
