1073
01:40:13,572 --> 01:40:16,160
"Upon this rock, I
will build my church."

1074
01:40:16,212 --> 01:40:18,680
"Or bring it down upon itself."

1075
01:40:19,480 --> 01:40:22,680
The bomb. It's in St. Peter's tomb.

1076
01:40:37,080 --> 01:40:38,588
The grid is still cycling.

1077
01:40:38,640 --> 01:40:40,560
The power to this section must be down.

1078
01:41:26,200 --> 01:41:29,000
It must be here. It must be.

1079
01:41:39,800 --> 01:41:40,960
Don't touch it.

1080
01:41:42,480 --> 01:41:44,040
We have seven minutes.

1081
01:41:49,960 --> 01:41:52,120
Robert, hold this.

1082
01:42:31,440 --> 01:42:33,880
It's cold down here, isn't it?

1083
01:42:33,932 --> 01:42:35,240
What's wrong?

1084
01:42:35,360 --> 01:42:37,880
Cold decreases battery life.

1085
01:42:39,880 --> 01:42:43,200
- We may have less than five minutes.
- So?

1086
01:42:43,240 --> 01:42:46,120
If I pull the power with
less than five minutes...

1087
01:42:46,172 --> 01:42:49,080
the residual charge
won't hold suspension.

1088
01:42:50,200 --> 01:42:52,080
We should leave it here
and get clear if we can.

1089
01:42:52,132 --> 01:42:53,280
At least down here the damage-

1090
