02:02:48,920 --> 02:02:52,480
And it's our understanding
that you require this text

1234
02:02:52,532 --> 02:02:54,960
to complete your scholary work.

1235
02:02:56,200 --> 02:03:01,000
We ask only that in your
last grand testament

1236
02:03:01,080 --> 02:03:03,880
you ensure it finds its way home.

1237
02:03:06,280 --> 02:03:07,640
Of course.

1238
02:03:07,840 --> 02:03:09,800
And when you write of us,

1239
02:03:09,920 --> 02:03:12,600
and you will write of us,

1240
02:03:12,840 --> 02:03:14,760
may I ask one thing?

1241
02:03:15,280 --> 02:03:17,000
Do so gently.

1242
02:03:19,040 --> 02:03:20,480
I'll try.

1243
02:03:20,800 --> 02:03:22,480
Religion is flawed,

1244
02:03:23,160 --> 02:03:25,920
but only because man is flawed.

1245
02:03:25,972 --> 02:03:28,680
All men, including this one.

1246
02:03:43,240 --> 02:03:45,160
He chose the name Luke.

1247
02:03:47,800 --> 02:03:50,880
There's been many Marks and Johns.

1248
02:03:51,960 --> 02:03:53,840
Never a Luke.

1249
02:03:54,200 --> 02:03:56,320
It said he was a doctor.

1250
02:03:56,800 --> 02:04:00,320
It's quite a message.
Science and faith, all in one.

1251
02:04:01,200 --> 02:04:03,280
The world is in need of both.

1252
02:04:05,000 --> 02:04:07,120
You'll counsel him wisely.

1253
02:04:08,000 --> 02:04:10,760
I'm an old man.
I'll counsel him briefly.

1254
02:04:16,600 --> 02:04:18,480
Mr. Langdon.

1255
02:04:23,480 --> 02:04:28,200
Thanks be to God for sending
someone to protect this church.

1256
02:04:32,160 --> 02:04:35,480
I don't believe He sent me, Father.

1257
02:04:35,560 --> 02:04:37,120
Oh, my son.

1258
02:04:37,560 --> 02:04:39,480
Of course He did.

